summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2794 for the improvement of Twenty-sixth Avenue Southwest, from West Brandon Street to West Andover Street, all in the City of Seattle, by planking the same, under Ordinance No. 33449, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
